OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1772565071
OL,3,CLeonardo factory secures #1bn contract
OL,4,Cto build defence helicopters
OL,6,FLeonardo in Yeovil has secured a one
OL,7,Fbillion pound contract to build a
OL,8,Ffleet of defence helicopters which
OL,9,Fwill support operations around the
OL,10,Fglobe.
OL,12,FFollowing days of speculation and
OL,13,Fmonths of uncertainty, the Ministry of
OL,14,FDefence confirmed that more than 3,000
OL,15,Fhighly skilled jobs have been saved at
OL,16,Fthe site, in a major helicopter deal
OL,17,Fthat will make Britain Leonardo's
OL,18,Fglobal centre for military helicopter
OL,19,Fproduction and exports.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
