OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1772565071
OL,3,CLeonardo factory secures #1bn contract
OL,4,Cto build defence helicopters
OL,6,FIt added that the production at the
OL,7,Fcountry's only specialist factory is
OL,8,Fworth "a potential #15 billion in UK
OL,9,Fexports over the next decade".
OL,11,FA fleet of 23 defence helicopters will
OL,12,Fnow be built in Yeovil, which could
OL,13,Fwork alongside uncrewed aircraft,
OL,14,Fpaving the path for future military
OL,15,Finternational orders to be built in
OL,16,Fthe UK.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1772565071
OL,3,CLeonardo factory secures #1bn contract
OL,4,Cto build defence helicopters
OL,6,FThe Ministry of Defence added: "The
OL,7,Fnew deal secured by the Government
OL,8,Fwith Leonardo will provide the UK
OL,9,FArmed Forces with 23 new medium-lift
OL,10,Fhelicopters.
OL,12,F"There are around 20 countries with
OL,13,Frequirements for new medium-lift
OL,14,Fhelicopters. Together with Leonardo's
OL,15,Fother helicopters, international
OL,16,Forders for NMH could generate over #15
OL,17,Fbillion in exports over the next 10
OL,18,Fyears.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1772565071
OL,3,CLeonardo factory secures #1bn contract
OL,4,Cto build defence helicopters
OL,6,F"The agreement secures the future of
OL,7,Fthe UK's sovereign helicopter
OL,8,Fproduction and Leonardo's facility in
OL,9,FYeovil, Somerset, sustaining 3,300
OL,10,Fjobs.
OL,12,F"This includes 650 people working
OL,13,Fdirectly on NMH and more involved with
OL,14,Fautonomous systems and providing
OL,15,Fongoing support and manufacture of the
OL,16,FMerlin and Wildcat helicopter fleets.
OL,18,F"With a UK supply chain of nearly 70
OL,19,Fcompanies, the programme also secures
OL,20,Fsovereign defence skills and expertise
OL,21,Ffor decades to come.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1772565071
OL,3,CLeonardo factory secures #1bn contract
OL,4,Cto build defence helicopters
OL,6,F"The deal represents a major
OL,7,Finvestment into the UK's industrial
OL,8,Fbase ` a key pillar of delivery for
OL,9,Fthe Defence Industrial Strategy and
OL,10,Fother growth-driving sectors like
OL,11,FAdvanced Manufacturing and Digital and
OL,12,FTechnology."
OL,14,F'A very good day for our town', says
OL,15,FAdam Dance MP
OL,17,FYeovil's MP, Adam Dance, says he's
OL,18,Fbeen petitioning the Government to
OL,19,Faward the contract for months.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1772565071
OL,3,CLeonardo factory secures #1bn contract
OL,4,Cto build defence helicopters
OL,6,FSpeaking to ITV West Country, he said:
OL,7,F"This is really, really great news for
OL,8,FYeovil and the surrounding area, but
OL,9,Flet's not forget we shouldn't have
OL,10,Fbeen put in this corner, this should
OL,11,Fhave been dealt with long ago.
OL,13,F"Let's not forget it has been a
OL,14,Fdifficult 18 months, not just for
OL,15,Fmyself, but for Leonardo. I felt
OL,16,Freally bad for the staff... It's been
OL,17,Freally unstable for people's lives.
OL,19,F"I am very over the moon that this has
OL,20,Fbeen delivered, but it has taken a lot
OL,21,Fof time"
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1772565071
OL,3,CLeonardo factory secures #1bn contract
OL,4,Cto build defence helicopters
OL,6,FIn a statement on Facebook, he added:
OL,7,F"I have worked tirelessly on this -
OL,8,Fsecuring debates, asking Urgent
OL,9,FQuestions, meeting Ministers and
OL,10,FLeonardo's leadership, and pressing
OL,11,Fthe case at every opportunity.
OL,13,F"I have consistently made clear that
OL,14,Fthis contract is vital for Yeovil and
OL,15,Ffor our national security. This
OL,16,Fdecision protects more than 3,000
OL,17,Fhighly skilled jobs in Yeovil,
OL,18,Fsupports thousands more in the supply
OL,19,Fchain, and secures the UK's only end-
OL,20,Fto-end helicopter manufacturing site.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1772565071
OL,3,CLeonardo factory secures #1bn contract
OL,4,Cto build defence helicopters
OL,6,F"It is a strong vote of confidence in
OL,7,Four workforce and in Yeovil's future.
OL,8,FToday is a very good day for our town."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
